subject: Rajasthan History
question_en: Who is the first Jat Raja of Marwar?
question_hi: मर्वा के पहले जात राजकीय कौन थी।
explanation_en:
Prithviraj Chauhan is considered as the first Jat Raja of Marwar. He was a prominent Hindu king during the 12th century and ruled over Marwar region.
